==Judicial branch==
The Supreme Court of Rwanda is the highest judicial power in Rwanda.  It and the High Council of the Judiciary oversee the courts of lower ordinary jurisdictions and courts of the special jurisdictions in Rwanda.

==Administrative divisions==
Rwanda has 5 provinces: [[Kigali Province]], [[Northern Province, Rwanda|Northern Province]], [[Eastern Province, Rwanda|Eastern Province]], [[Southern Province, Rwanda|Southern Province]] and [[Western Province, Rwanda|Western Province]].

