Rwanda joined the [[Commonwealth of Nations]] in 2009, making the country one of only two in the Commonwealth without a [[British Empire|British colonial past]];<ref>http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/8384930.stm</ref> the other being the former [[Portuguese Empire|Portuguese colony]] [[Mozambique]].

